    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Botinator: A physics‑driven FPS adventure game blending combat, destruction and puzzle mechanics. Play as a lone technician sent to uncover the cause of a facility’s sudden radio silence. Unravel the mystery behind the madness by blasting robotic creatures into pieces. Improvise with the environment  to survive down the deepest paths of the facility. Where is the source of all trouble? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight. Break. Solve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics driven interactions and breakable objects. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/22500fee4dd96675e827586429b94b08.poster.avif?t=1769205784\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/22500fee4dd96675e827586429b94b08.webm?t=1769205784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/22500fee4dd96675e827586429b94b08.mp4?t=1769205784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced movement and responsive enemy behaviour. Watch out, they’re good at climbing!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/efb03348b5ae2227c61f9e2106837d01.poster.avif?t=1769205784\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/efb03348b5ae2227c61f9e2106837d01.webm?t=1769205784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/efb03348b5ae2227c61f9e2106837d01.mp4?t=1769205784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every scenario plays out different, handle them in your own way. Stealthing, shooting or simply throwing stuff at the problem can all be good solutions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/8137a1f6ac59218318449424cff7442f.poster.avif?t=1769205784\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/8137a1f6ac59218318449424cff7442f.webm?t=1769205784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/8137a1f6ac59218318449424cff7442f.mp4?t=1769205784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break up the combat with short puzzle and story sequences. Wire electricity and figure out whats really going on down in the lowest sections.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/66cbe791fcabf64197e7e90675c20408.poster.avif?t=1769205784\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/66cbe791fcabf64197e7e90675c20408.webm?t=1769205784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258920/extras/66cbe791fcabf64197e7e90675c20408.mp4?t=1769205784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Community</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built-in leaderboard to share your fastest playthroughs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
